==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Astounding
<hw>As*tound"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of a nature to astound;
astonishing; amazing; <as>as, an <ex>astounding</ex> force, statement,
or fact</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>As*tound"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Astoundment</ent>⟦br⟧
